 &lt;line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12">&lt;/line>
 &lt;/svg>&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;code>src&lt;/code> : Source of the resource. It can be one of three&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Admonition Shortcode</title><link>https://1bl4z3r.github.io/hermit-V2/en/posts/admonition-shortcode/</link><pubDate>Fri, 20 Oct 2023 20:06:06 +0530</pubDate><guid>https://1bl4z3r.github.io/hermit-V2/en/posts/admonition-shortcode/</guid><description>&lt;p>The &lt;code>admonition&lt;/code> shortcode supports &lt;strong>8&lt;/strong> types of banners to help you put a notice on your page.&lt;/p>
